Li ya ce, "Kungiyar Kimiyya ta Kasa ta kasar Sin tana ba da tallafi ga cibiyoyin ilimi a hanyar da ta yi kama da yadda wasu hukumomin gwamnati, kamar National Science Foundation na Amurka, ke ba masu bincike a Amurka kudi kadan kadan, amma kasar Sin ba ta da ingancin aikin kimiyya.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta kafa Cibiyar Haɗin Kai ta Artificial Intelligence don haɗa kan masana'antu da abokan hulɗa a cikin ilimi, kuma Fadar White House ta sanar da kafa Kwamitin Zaɓin kan Ilimin Artificial.
