Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10-6 a wasan karshe na gasar Ryder Cup
Turai za ta samu babban ci gaba a wasan karshe na gasar Ryder Cup bayan ta doke Amurka da ci 10 da 6 a wasan kwallon kafa da kuma wasan Fossum a ranar Asabar.
Duka biyu masu motsawa Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci wannan tashin hankali tare da cin nasara biyu akan Tiger Woods wanda ke gwagwarmaya don ƙara maki huɗu zuwa rikodin har yanzu a Le Golf National.
