A shafi na farko na "Sunday Morning" an rubuta: 30 ga Satumba, 1882, yau ne shekara 136 da ta gabata, kuma a Jamus ne aka haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi na gaba Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger.
Geiger ya kirkiro hanyar ganowa da auna abubuwa masu saurin yaduwa, wani abu da ya haifar da na'urar da aka sani da Geiger Counter.
Daga bisani, Geiger Coefficient, wanda ya kasance cibiyar kimiyya, ya zama cibiyar al'adu a cikin fim din 1950 "The Bell of Coronado", inda Roy Rogers da Dale Evans suka fito a matsayin masanin kimiyya na kauye:
Mutum: "Mene ne wannan?"
Rogers: "Wannan Geiger Coefficient ne da ake amfani da shi wajen gano inda ma'adanai masu saurin gudu kamar uranium suke.
Idan ka sa kunnuwan kunne, za ka iya jin tasirin atomatik da ke fitowa daga radiation na ma'adinai.
Evans: "Oh, yanzu yana fashewa!"
Hans Geiger ya mutu a 1945, kwanaki kadan kafin ranar haihuwarsa ta 63.
