HIV/AIDS: China ta sanar da karuwar sabbin masu cutar da kashi 14 cikin dari
China ta sanar da karuwar yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Hukumomin kiwon lafiya sun ce mutane sama da 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a kasar.
A cikin kwata na biyu na shekara ta 2018, an samu kusan sabbin mutane 40,000 da suka kamu da cutar.
Yawancin sabbin cututtukan sun kamu ne ta hanyar jima'i, kuma wannan ya nuna cewa abubuwa sun bambanta da na baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV ta yadu cikin sauri a wasu yankunan kasar Sin sakamakon kamuwa da cutar ta jini.
Amma hukumomin kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin sun ce a wani taro da aka yi a birnin Winan, an samu raguwar yawan masu dauke da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar.
Amma a kasar Sin, yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya karu da 100,000 a kowace shekara.
Yaduwar cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT a China.
An haramta aikata luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma nuna bambanci ga mutanen LGBT ya zama ruwan dare gama gari.
Saboda tsattsauran ra'ayi a kasar, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin dari na maza da suka yi jima'i da maza za su auri mata.
Yawancin cututtuka suna zuwa daga rashin kariya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan dangantaka.
Tun daga 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar HIV ga kowa a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
