Jakadan Amurka ya zargi Beijing da amfani da kafofin yada labaran Amurka don yada farfaganda mako guda bayan da jaridar kasar Sin ta buga tallace-tallace na shafi hudu a jaridar Amurka don amfanin cinikin Amurka da Sin.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana a ranar Laraba a jaridar Des Moines Register, babbar jaridar da aka fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa, game da tallafin da aka biya ta China Daily bayan da ta zargi China da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka na ranar 6 ga Nuwamba.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa China na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka ya sa jami'an Amurka suka ce a wata hira da suka yi da kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters cewa Washington ta kirkiro wata sabuwar hanyar matsa lamba kan kasar Sin.
Ko da yake al'ada ce ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su rika tallatawa juna domin bunkasa kasuwanci, amma yanzu kasar Sin da Amurka suna cikin yakin cinikayya da ke kara tsanantawa, inda suke ganin ana saka haraji kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa da su.
A farkon yakin cinikayya, kasar Sin ta ce harajin da ta dauka na mayar da martani ga manyan masu fitar da kayayyaki ne kamar Ayo, wadanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Trump ta Republican da masana kasar Sin da Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a Amurka da kuma gwamnan jihar Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona na kasar Sin, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
