An kafa shirin yanar gizo na duniya don samar da sabuwar intanet don sayen Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo mai fadi, yana kafa wani sabon kamfani don yin gasa da Facebook, Amazon, da Google.
Sabon aikin wannan almara na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne wanda ya dogara da dandamali na buɗe tushen tushen Solid na Berners Lee.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma wanda zai iya samun damar shiga.
A wata hira da ya yi da Fast Company, Barnes Lee ya yi dariya cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
