Kungiyar Turai ta doke Amurka da ci 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a wasan karshe na Ryder Cup na 2018 a Le Golf National a bayan Paris, Faransa.
Amurka ta sha kashi shida a jere a gasar Ryder Cup da ke yanzu a Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar Turai ba tun 1993.
Kungiyar Thomas Beecham ta Denmark ta samu maki 14.5 da ake bukata domin cin nasarar Amurka.
